  "instructions": [
    "Combine flour, baking powder, salt, and black pepper in a bowl. Whisk until well combined.",
    "Add caraway seeds and mix well.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together olive oil, onion, garlic, and hot sauce.",
    "Add the wet ingredients to the dry ingredients and stir until just combined.",
    "Heat a non-stick pan or griddle over medium heat.",
    "Drop the batter by 1/4 cupfuls onto the pan.",
    "Cook for 2-3 minutes or until the edges start to curl and the surface is dry.",
    "Flip and cook for another 2 minutes.",
    "Serve hot with a dollop of sour cream or applesauce.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh herbs if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
